{"tid":123313,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)戰狼300 1-2","createTime":"2017-02-16T18:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T20:59:01.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dfd6cf6a1965b3d2a13793a1a37ba365b4dd5fa","tid":123313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:13:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6d021b2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=fb3d56b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/5c/300poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F5c%2F300poster.jpg&h=2f9fbc25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://m.popkey.co/8cfba7/R4D1d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.popkey.co%2F8cfba7%2FR4D1d.gif&h=5307ef4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.電影《300壯士：斯巴達的逆襲》忠實改編自法蘭克&middot;米勒的視覺文學《300》，內容描述斯巴達國王列奧尼達一世和300名斯巴達戰士奮力對抗波斯帝國的薛西斯一世和他的大軍。面對懸殊的人數差距，斯巴達戰士的犧牲鼓舞了所有希臘人，讓他們團結起來對抗波斯大軍的入侵。電影的故事大致根據西元前480年9月發生的希波戰爭之溫泉關戰役改編..<br />\n<br />\n2.講述在「300壯士」故事發生十年前，以及故事發生之後，薛西斯一世成為波斯帝國國王，他繼承父親的意志遠征希臘，因此引發了兩方之間激烈的戰爭。年輕勇猛的女性阿爾特米西亞擔任波斯海軍領導人，同特米慾謀力領導的雅典軍人在海戰中對決。在雙方的第一次較量中雅典方面大敗，特米慾謀力隨後建議放棄雅典城，並尋求同樣遭受波斯重創的斯巴達人的幫助。最後在薩拉米灣海戰中，雅典軍隊聯合斯巴達的歌果女王率領的戰士，打敗波斯海軍，特米慾謀力並親手殺死阿爾特米西亞，接著他們一同向薛西斯一世的波斯大軍前進.....<br />\n<br />\n2 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9da4bce06f1ca288b53624b694f56ec685785f","tid":123313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57a79a929dca661851bf97e9a7063a7a026ae5b","tid":123313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c86c961ed08606e18e4cf6213926014c4ea77e5","tid":123313,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:20:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e82c20071e774737a017f957d94d8d6190b17b6","tid":123313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce261da3edbeb62d2b49a743db560d12c5a5e75a","tid":123313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T20:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5f4f37c48687c2ecdd34c6c9600216be70adc7","tid":123313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T20:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}